          <p>To help answer these questions and demonstrate the importance of Great Britain’s Twitter conversations, Altius have created a data driven and 
            machine-learnt solution. Across the UK and at a given County level you can interact and track how popular a political party is on Twitter.</p>
          <p>For more information on Altius and to find out how we created this solution please <a id="linkToContact" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#section3"><b>scroll down</b>here</a></p>
